y0","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8ICghu6zqaTFeW","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8ICghu6zqaTFeW","target":"rec0MJooZFfHsxW1N","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec4qfLjUoZ97wgqt","ref":"Amos.7.1","text":"Thus hath the Lord GOD shewed unto me; and, behold, he formed grasshoppers in the beginning of the shooting up of the latter growth; and, lo, it was the latter growth after the king’s mowings.","year":-787},{"id":"recskbzxa3mWzc14n","ref":"Amos.7.2","text":"And it came to pass, that when they had made an end of eating the grass of the land, then I said, O Lord GOD, forgive, I beseech thee: by whom shall Jacob arise? for he is small.","year":-787},{"id":"recWkhKRoKfSLLZs5","ref":"Amos.7.3","text":"The LORD repented for this: It shall not be, saith the LORD.","year":-787},{"id":"rectetggDIiIiEvSP","ref":"Amos.7.4","text":"Thus hath the Lord GOD shewed unto me: and, behold, the Lord GOD called to contend by fire, and it devoured the great deep, and did eat up a part.","year":-787},{"id":"recJTu10x86qg0rfH","ref":"Amos.7.5","text":"Then said I, O Lord GOD, cease, I beseech thee: by whom shall Jacob arise? for he is small.","year":-787},{"id":"recZjTp3rsDO4MOJW","ref":"Amos.7.6","text":"The LORD repented for this: This also shall not be, saith the Lord GOD.","year":-787},{"id":"recElUXl8oxX1GMLb","ref":"Amos.7.7","text":"Thus he shewed me: and, behold, the Lord stood upon a wall made by a plumbline, with a plumbline in his hand.","year":-787},{"id":"rec9sVKpJx0cxbc4X","ref":"Amos.7.8","text":"And the LORD said unto me, Amos, what seest thou? And I said, A plumbline. Then said the Lord, Behold, I will set a plumbline in the midst of my people Israel: I will not again pass by them any more:","year":-787}]}
